<item>
            <title>[SOLR-17075] Ref Guide link checking not enabled in &quot;gradle check&quot; by default</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17075</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This was a bug introduced in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16747&quot; title=&quot;Remove git requirement for gradle build&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-16747&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-16747&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; that made it so the ref guide was not built with &lt;tt&gt;gradle check&lt;/tt&gt;, and thus links were also not checked by default.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;This means there are a few problems with the ref guide in the last two releases. I&apos;ll fix those problems, and backport the necessary fixes for the 9.3 and 9.4 ref guides.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
